{
  "stem": "5559.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You can dream all night about something, but it didn't help much.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was taken with all the youngster to Nikolaev.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is called Nikolaev on the Bug.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Bug, B-U-G-- this is a big river there, an industrial city strictly occupied that was already-- not Romanian-- German city.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Bug, industrial city.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not Bug-- Bug is a-- Nikolaev-- Nikolaev is the equivalent of industrial city.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In those day, you can say Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, Pittsburgh-- big.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there, where we were taken for plain labor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They put us in barracks, below, like, you know, in little barracks, what you call where you put potatoes, you know, with that one roof.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You cannot lift your head.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they have two shelters, one on top the other.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You lay next to each other, you keep warm?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in the morning, before it gets light, you're marching out-- no clothes also, whatever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You're marching out to work, whatever is there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Most of the time, heavy snow, so there was no-- the big tractors, like, you have here, shovel to get the snow.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You were the tractors-- hundreds and hundreds of youngsters with shovel make the snow so the tanks can pass, right?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they-- and they gave you in the morning [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 100 gram, they call it, of bread, and a little dish of soup.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If I may, I'd like to describe that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The bread was made out of red kernels, which, if you ever saw a straw broom, they have red kernels-- real, not the nylon brooms which you use-- the real straw out of red kernels.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was grinded.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As soon as you got the bread, hot bread, it got green.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They call it [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's 100% poison.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
